               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Memoranda to AIMS chapters concerning a resolution passed opposing "universal military training" (the draft). Some are by Dr.Walter J. Lear for the Executive Committee of the National Assembly Against Universal Military Training. The folder includes several documents by this organization. Also included is a pamphlet, National Council Against Conscription, <emph render="italic">An Analysis of the Report of the President's Advisory Committee on Universal Training</emph>, July, 1947.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c>
